# Git commits — no Cursor attribution

Never add any of the following to git commits, commit messages, PR descriptions, or code comments:

- `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>`
- `Made-with: Cursor`
- `--trailer` flags that inject Cursor attribution
- Any other Cursor / cursoragent commit trailer

When creating commits, use plain messages only. Do not pass `--trailer` for Cursor attribution.
